latestPosts.caption:
ESSNCE, we need to have a word…

Do y’all read minds? I’m now over here wondering why this doesn’t have my name written all over it, ‘cause I think this was specifically made for ME 😮‍💨

Isn’t it funny how I was convinced I hated strawberry in perfumery? Ever since Kayali released Yum Boujee Marshmallow I fell head over heels for that creamy strawberry DNA and I’m SO happy this juicy fruit is a trend now! 🤭 

Is it the same as YBM? No! But it definitely has similarities as strawberry is the main character here. 

Strawberry Eclaire smells creamy and pastry-like 🥮 with the strawberry leaning more to the jammy side. I might even say it has a soft bubblegum vibe to it - it kinda smells nostalgic and I’m all here for it 🩷

@essnce.edp thank you for sending this my wayyyy 😍

latestPosts.caption:
the scream I scrumpt when I smelled this perfume by Paris Corner… oh my dayzzzz!

For YEARS I’ve hoped that there’d be a perfume version of one of my all time favorite body mists…Cheirosa ‘71! 

I’ve seen the brand release a perfume of ‘62 which is SAID to be the most popular/best selling SdJ scent (which is craaaazy to me bc ‘71 is THE ONE 🤭) and I kept praying for them to do the same for my baby…

My prayers have been answered! 😍 Molten Caramel by Paris Corner is EXACTLY what I was looking for! 

Tbh I don’t know if it’s an actual shmoop, but to my nose they’re 99.9999% the same and I genuinely couldn’t be happier 😭🫶🏼 

I haven’t reached for anything else ever since I got Molten Caramel and I loooove layering them for some extra zhuzh (as @roxslayofficial would say) 🩷

Are you picking this up? 😏

@pariscornerperfumes - thank youuuu from the bottom of my heart for creating this and sending it my way! 😩😂💕

latestPosts.caption:
👼🏼 SMELL ANGELIC 👼🏼 

I’ve been loving musks lately and so I figured to dedicate a post to all my faves as of right now 💅

🪽 Kashmir Musk by Arabian Oud

This leaves the most gorgeous scent trail! It’s show stopping honestly. The dent says it all 🤭

🪽 Arabians Musk by Montale*

This might be my favorite Montale perfume, though Oud Sapparot 🍍 might take its spot 😏 Arabians Musk is a musk that really stands out and is perfect for those who love a sweeter, classic perfume. 

🪽 Musk Pomegranate mukhammaria by Gulf Orchid*

If you haven’t heard of mukhammaria yet, you’re missing out! A solid perfume with the consistency of soft vaseline. Also… this is STRONG! 💪🏼 You don’t even need to layer it with anything else for great projection. 

For more mukhammarias >>> @missluxurious_hq 🌸

🪽 Musk Tahara by El Nabil*

An intimate musk. I’ve read it’s been used by women for their intimate zones for centuries! 😮 

🪽 Angel Musk by Gulf Orchid*

Probably my favorite musk of ALL time! I’ve said it before and I feel like nothing compares to this. A spicy & sexy musk - and affordable too! 🫦 

🪽 Musk | 12 by Kayali

As said: super crisp! This is so elegant 🫶🏼 I can see why people are begging for this perfume to be restocked. Kayali & Mona… I’m looking atchu 👀 

Tell me what your favorite musk is in the comments and as always…

Don’t forget to like, share & save for later! 🎀
